title: Maunakea observatories welcome Hawaiʻi residents (The University of Hawaii System)
text: ( Source : The University of Hawaii System ) President Barack Obama at the White House Astronomy Night in Washington, D.C. on October 19 , 2015 . The Maunakea Observatories and ʻImiloa Astronomy Center will offer the Kamaʻāina Observatory
